ginivision/net.gini.android.vision.internal.ui/CustomFontTextView

CustomFontTextView

public class CustomFontTextView extends AppCompatTextView
Content copied to clipboard

Internal use only. Custom TextView with an additional 'gvCustomFont' attribute. System font names or font file paths (full path in the assets folder) can be used. 

   <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
      xmlns:gini="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
      android:layout_width="match_parent"
      android:layout_height="match_parent"
      android:orientation="vertical">

      <net.gini.android.vision.ui.CustomFontTextView
          android:id="@+id/giniTextView"
          android:layout_width="wrap_content"
          android:layout_height="wrap_content"
          gini:gvCustomFont="sans-serif-light" />
  </LinearLayout>

 <net.gini.android.vision.ui.CustomFontTextView
     gini:gvCustomFont="myFonts/Cave-Story.ttf" />
